From: Carlos Eduardo Arango Gutierrez <eduardoa@nvidia.com>
Date: Tue, 2 Dec 2025 09:26:44 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] [no-relnote] Update Go download URL to official go.dev/dl
 endpoint

Signed-off-by: Carlos Eduardo Arango Gutierrez <eduardoa@nvidia.com>
---
 deployments/container/Dockerfile | 2 +-
 docker/Dockerfile.debian         | 2 +-
 docker/Dockerfile.opensuse-leap  | 2 +-
 docker/Dockerfile.rpm-yum        | 2 +-
 docker/Dockerfile.ubuntu         | 2 +-
 5 files changed, 5 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/deployments/container/Dockerfile b/deployments/container/Dockerfile
index 9dc286e0a..d02492432 100644
--- a/deployments/container/Dockerfile
+++ b/deployments/container/Dockerfile
@@ -35,7 +35,7 @@ RUN set -eux; \
         aarch64 | arm64) ARCH='arm64' ;; \
         *) echo "unsupported architecture" ; exit 1 ;; \
     esac; \
-    wget -nv -O - https://storage.googleapis.com/golang/go${GOLANG_VERSION}.linux-${ARCH}.tar.gz \
+    wget -nv -O - https://go.dev/dl/go${GOLANG_VERSION}.linux-${ARCH}.tar.gz \
     | tar -C /usr/local -xz
 
 
